children.alt: Falafel with Dill sauce and Tabbouleh

children.value:
<Recipe>
[1] Boil: 3/4 cups water
[2] Remove from heat: #1
[3] Cook: 1/2 cup couscous, #2
[4] Chop finely: 4 firm roma tomatoes, 1 english cucumber, 2 bunches parsley, 4 green onions
[5] Combine: #4, 2 tbsp dried mint (or 15 leaves fresh)
[6] Mix together: #3, #5, 1/4 tsp salt, 4 tbsp lemon juice, 4 tbsp olive oil
</Recipe>
